  "prompt": "What is a teacher?",
  "response": "A teacher is a professional who educates and instructs students in a school, college, university, or other educational setting. Their key responsibilities include:\n\n1. Delivering curriculum and academic content\n2. Helping students learn and develop knowledge and skills\n3. Providing guidance and support for students' intellectual and personal growth\n4. Assessing student progress through tests, assignments, and evaluations\n5. Creating lesson plans and engaging learning activities\n6. Managing classroom behavior and creating a positive learning environment\n7. Supporting individual student needs and learning styles\n8. Inspiring and motivating students to achieve their potential\n\nTeachers can work at various levels, such as:\n- Early childhood/preschool\n- Elementary school\n- Middle school\n- High school\n- College/university\n- Specialized education (special needs, vocational training)\n\nThey play a crucial role in society by helping to educate and shape future generations.",
